### SCARNERGY v2.0 — API Test Suite
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension
### Set @token to your JWT after signing in

@baseUrl = http://localhost:54321
@anonKey = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpc3MiOiJzdXBhYmFzZS1kZW1vIiwicm9sZSI6ImFub24iLCJleHAiOjE5ODM4MTI5OTZ9.CRFA0NiK7ACcPjLjK9CkOs8hL32t6nO2E-pUaF5Gp3A
@token = REPLACE_WITH_JWT_AFTER_LOGIN

### ─── AUTH ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Sign up
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/v1/signup
Content-Type: application/json
apikey: {{anonKey}}

{
  "email": "inspector@krontiva.nl",
  "password": "TestPassword123!",
  "data": {
    "full_name": "Jan de Vries",
    "org_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
    "role": "inspector"
  }
}

###

### Sign in — copy access_token to @token above
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/v1/token?grant_type=password
Content-Type: application/json
apikey: {{anonKey}}

{
  "email": "inspector@krontiva.nl",
  "password": "TestPassword123!"
}

### ─── ORGANISATIONS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get own organisation
GET {{baseUrl}}/rest/v1/organisations?select=*
apikey: {{anonKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─── BUILDINGS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### List all buildings in org
GET {{baseUrl}}/rest/v1/buildings?select=*,zones(id,zone_code,name)&order=created_at.desc
apikey: {{anonKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get building summary view
GET {{baseUrl}}/rest/v1/building_summary?select=*
apikey: {{anonKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Create a new building
POST {{baseUrl}}/rest/v1/buildings
Content-Type: application/json
apikey: {{anonKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Prefer: return=representation

{
  "org_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "street": "Keizersgracht",
  "house_number": "123",
  "postal_code": "1017 DK",
  "city": "Amsterdam",
  "building_type": "residential_single",
  "construction_year": 1910,
  "gross_floor_area_m2": 85
}

### ─── ZONES ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### List zones for a building
GET {{baseUrl}}/rest/v1/zones?building_id=eq.b0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001&select=*,building_elements(*)
apikey: {{anonKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─── BLE DEVICES ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### List devices
GET {{baseUrl}}/rest/v1/ble_devices?select=*&order=last_connected_at.desc
apikey: {{anonKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Register a new GLM device
POST {{baseUrl}}/rest/v1/ble_devices
Content-Type: application/json
apikey: {{anonKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Prefer: return=representation

{
  "org_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "device_type": "bosch_glm50c",
  "mac_address": "AA:BB:CC:DD:EE:FF",
  "nickname": "My GLM 50C"
}

### ─── INSPECTION SESSIONS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Start a new session
POST {{baseUrl}}/rest/v1/inspection_sessions
Content-Type: application/json
apikey: {{anonKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Prefer: return=representation

{
  "org_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "building_id": "b0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "inspector_id": "REPLACE_WITH_YOUR_USER_ID"
}

###

### Close a session (Edge Function)
POST {{baseUrl}}/functions/v1/session_close
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "session_id": "REPLACE_WITH_SESSION_ID"
}

### ─── MEASUREMENTS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Insert a measurement
POST {{baseUrl}}/rest/v1/measurements
Content-Type: application/json
apikey: {{anonKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Prefer: return=representation

{
  "org_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "session_id": "REPLACE_WITH_SESSION_ID",
  "device_id": "d0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "inspector_id": "REPLACE_WITH_YOUR_USER_ID",
  "element_id": "e0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "value_mm": 2750,
  "unit": "mm",
  "measurement_type": "wall_height",
  "ingestion_path": "mobile"
}

###

### Query recent measurements
GET {{baseUrl}}/rest/v1/recent_measurements?limit=20
apikey: {{anonKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─── EDGE FUNCTIONS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Validate measurements batch
POST {{baseUrl}}/functions/v1/measurement_validate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "measurements": [
    { "id": "REPLACE", "value_mm": 2750, "measurement_type": "wall_height", "session_id": "REPLACE" },
    { "id": "REPLACE", "value_mm": -100, "measurement_type": "wall_width", "session_id": "REPLACE" }
  ]
}

###

### Compute energy labels for a building
POST {{baseUrl}}/functions/v1/energy_label_estimate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "building_id": "b0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001"
}

### ─── RPC CALLS ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Compute energy label for a zone
POST {{baseUrl}}/rest/v1/rpc/compute_zone_energy_label
Content-Type: application/json
apikey: {{anonKey}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "p_zone_id": "z0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001"
}
